{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "aeecfb5d-1850-4689-b5d8-112bfda14647", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/aeecfb5d-1850-4689-b5d8-112bfda14647@2.pkg/1772602428935/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602429709", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/aeecfb5d-1850-4689-b5d8-112bfda14647@2.pkg/1772602428935/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602429709"}, "identifier": "aeecfb5d-1850-4689-b5d8-112bfda14647", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B.</span><span>有误，&ldquo;欲扬先抑&rdquo;应为托物言志的写法。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对课文《爱莲说》内容理解不正确的一项是（ &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "对课文《爱莲说》内容理解不正确的一项是（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/aeecfb5d-1850-4689-b5d8-112bfda14647@2.pkg/item.json?v=1751941776798", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本文通过对莲可贵品格的赞美，含蓄地表达了作者的人生态度：既不愿像陶渊明那样消极避世，又不愿像世人那样追逐功名富贵，而是要在污浊的世间独立不移，永远保持清白。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>作者写莲花是为了写人，用莲花的高洁品质来象征君子高尚的品质。这是欲扬先抑的写法。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>以&ldquo;菊之爱&rdquo;&ldquo;牡丹之爱&rdquo;衬托&ldquo;莲之爱&rdquo;，突出莲的高洁质朴，赋予莲花美好的品质，同时表达作者洁身自好、不慕名利、正直伟岸的高尚情操。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>莲花是高洁的象征，它出淤泥而不染，清洁无瑕，故而中国人民喜欢以莲花的&ldquo;出淤泥而不染，濯清涟而不妖&rdquo;作为激励自己洁身自好的座右铭，而这一名句就出自北宋著名的哲学家周敦颐的《爱莲说》。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对课文《爱莲说》内容理解不正确的一项是（ &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342961", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, 